{"tid":1694973,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人幾時先接受支那蝗蟲係敵人？","createTime":"2019-11-05T11:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T15:46:36.000Z","uid":54303,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"687254abcb94c025f034c84d5bd727597cb49fac","tid":1694973,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T11:06:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/remonwangxt/status/1191589884244504576?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fremonwangxt%2Fstatus%2F1191589884244504576%3Fs%3D21&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=1f71bbbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fremonwangxt%2Fstatus%2F1191589884244504576%3Fs%3D21&h=d1dc35fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/remonwangxt/status/1191589884244504576?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己入去睇下有幾噁心。<br />\n除左少數明白事理但無乜實權既自由派之外，成個支那國都係想香港人死絕，想留地不留人。<br />\n而果少數清醒既人當中，亦有唔少係大中華膠，寧願香港同呢班充滿敵意既畜牲害蟲繼續做「同胞」，都唔會接受香港成為一個自由、獨立既國家。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醒下啦，香港唔將矛頭放去全部支那蝗，都唔洗旨意光復香港。<span style=\"color: red;\">尤其係香港做緊野既支共黨員，係破壞香港既罪魁禍首。</span>唔滅蟲只係死路一條，打幾多曱甴都吉唔中要害。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於有傻鳩想「將革命之火燒上大陸」？我同你講肯定唔會得，佢地只會因為自己利益受損而去維權，但絕對唔會因為其他人既利益、或者理念，而去抗爭。如果佢地明乜鳩叫自由，一早就反抗左啦。<span style=\"color: red;\">只要我地持續打擊支那經濟，就自然可以火燒大陸，</span>根本唔洗照顧支那蝗既感受。"},{"pid":"c3e3547ffc6cd9e31f105c6df260243e466213d1","tid":1694973,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:29:18.000Z","msg":"班畜牲準備移民歐美日本！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1694904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1694904</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"55792d8c7a36ff358442c8dddff6a55e6eba14cf","tid":1694973,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7be0544bf920eee43b339bec44464cfa61da4ed","tid":1694973,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T14:27:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090bb40c3fa0c10da72735f358a1b5a513654112","tid":1694973,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:10:43.000Z","msg":"好多藍屍都唔鍾意大劣人<br />\n只係對一國兩制仲有份信任<br />\n其實俾人溫水煮蛙<br />\n遲d死左都唔知咩事<br />\n<br />\n黃絲就有危機感，聞到燶味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9ca2662c910e8eb718755adda1775807abbe41","tid":1694973,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"090bb40c3fa0c10da72735f358a1b5a513654112","tid":1694973,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:10:43.000Z","msg":"好多藍屍都唔鍾意大劣人<br />\n只係對一國兩制仲有份信任<br />\n其實俾人溫水煮蛙<br />\n遲d死左都唔知咩事<br />\n<br />\n黃絲就有危機感，聞到燶味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:25:20.000Z","msg":"一國兩制死左好耐啦<br />\n而家係支那侵蝕香港既階段"},{"pid":"e8f3f5c900b6b3aaa0fd6569dd913ffc1076abe9","tid":1694973,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T04:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830ddcf1a618689d09aa3961760396763a196f37","tid":1694973,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}